1) How can deep learning techniques be effectively utilized to enhance the accuracy and 
efficiency of defect detection and classification in Betaguard Yellow sealing? 
2) What are the primary challenges in implementing an automated defect detection 
system for defect detection in Betaguard Yellow sealing using deep learning 
approaches, and how can these challenges be addressed? 
